### Context

Recommending user movies based on different parameters by taking input as movie name and giving the output as movie suggestions along with similarity score.


### Content

There are various metadata available in the above datasets, the user can accordingly choose a data from the above bunch of datasets and design his movie recommendation engine.

I would like to thank my College faculties for encouraging me to develop this project due to which I was able to create this dataset.
